│       runtime specification, the runtime must not perform a $PATH  │
│       lookup before executing the container process; it should     │
│       call execve instead, which does not search $PATH. The fix is │
│       to replace execvpe with execve so that the executable is     │
│       invoked exactly as given in the process arguments, failing   │
│       if it is not an absolute path. This preserves other existing │
│       behavior such as chdir and environment propagation.          │
